  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6815.9 sitting above the GEX flip at 6806, dealers are in positive gamma territory and will sell rallies into the massive +95.5B gamma wall at 6830. The PIN regime with strong positive gamma concentration between 6820-6830 creates a natural magnet effect, as dealers will aggressively hedge against any move toward these strikes by selling futures on strength. Watch 6806 as the critical pivot - any break below flips dealers to negative gamma where they'd accelerate selling, but the current setup favors mean reversion back toward the 6820-6830 zone.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pulled toward 6830 with dealers capping upside there.",
